<Layout 
  title="Maine Dispensary POS Systems" 
  description="Maine cannabis dispensary POS system guide. Metrc integration, inventory tracking, compliant transactions, and POS selection for 2026."
  heroImage="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1556742044-3c52d6e88c62?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=1200&h=400"
